    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Thanks for reporting @rstormsf! The `close` and `enableRefunds` functions you mentioned are called as part of `finalization` in `RefundableCrowdsale`. Take a look [here](https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/zeppelin-solidity/blob/5cf503673faea92c1b5c615c3f8358febf06e160/contracts/crowdsale/RefundableCrowdsale.sol#L47-L51).\r\n\r\nThe idea was to make it trustless, which is why only the crowdsale contract has the permissions to call them.\r\n\r\nIf you want to improve coverage it will be a very welcome PR!",
